ou just hold your brothers is all you did like you didn\'t do anything well shoot when I like three years four years old in you and then they had a whole like I know with the way we resent it and then I went in there one day and I can\'t lose and they were stealing and I beat him up that\'s not what happened all you just call mom Bess was in their earlier stages like the young like the you know the eighth the ninth of ten stages when I got to be living 12 like I had enough of it you know I\'m saying it was just like all right we\'re gonna battle until one of us just fall out like that was gonna happen so I mean we\'re not talking about the early stages dealt with then and then I got enough for doing that and just decided that you know that wasn\'t the way I was gonna go out if I was gonna go out at least I was gonna have some type of blood or or something on me so I can actually say I got him - very good I mean guys she was gonna be some type of me at each other but in a day that\'s that\'s what siblings do maybe was just a little bit more aggressive than other people but that\'s the message you had to have but we was always good and respectful with people and elders and what we did so it when I got out of hand too bad Josh probably wants a crack at you go ahead poppy what do you got yes gotten you gage a seat the limb drop me one of his sons thank you all right that\'s my father one man use a window shopper mad at me I think I know why man use a window shopper in the store looking at stuff you can buy man use a window shopper in the dealership trying to get a test-drive man use a window shopper mad at me when you see me right by [Music] time to play the game that is a fashion icon do you question you give us topics and events and we question them do you question they catch your safewords the catchers effort this is what we do around here we study journalism we get Disney to pay us we go to college softball Texas in Oklahoma and we determine whether the catcher is m